= SDL_ClearError =
Use this function to clear any previous error message.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_ClearError(void)
```

== Code Examples ==
```c++
const char *error = SDL_GetError();
if (*error) {
  printf("SDL_Error : %s\n", error);
  SDL_ClearError();
}
```

